text:
Rod Stewart teamed up with DNCE to re-release his mega hit "Da Ya Think I'm Sexy." Joe Jonas adds a great new dance vibe to the classic 70's song.

They plan to perform their new collaboration Sunday in Las Vegas and a live broadcast of their performance will be screened at the 2017 MTV VMAs.

Listen below!
title: Rod Stewart Re-Releases "Do Ya Think I'm Sexy" With DNCE!
